item.description:
Entrepreneurs sharing great ideas - that's what we're all about. This is not a venue for self-promotion networkers or get rich quick MLMers.

We're a small group of business owners (and sometimes busniness owner wannabes) sharing ideas on how to profitably run a business. Our meetings are very informal and fun.

Meeting attendance via RSVP only.
item.name: The Manchester, NH Entrepreneur April Meetup
